%!PS

%	This example appears in section "Add Bezier Curve to Current Path"
%	in Chapter 7 - "Arcs and Curves".
%

/inch { 72 mul } def			%  define inch procedure
/P0 { 1.0 inch 1.0 inch } def		%  first end point
/P1 { 1.0 inch 7.0 inch } def		%  first control point
/P2 { 5.0 inch 6.0 inch } def		%  second control point
/P3 { 7.0 inch 2.0 inch } def		%  second end point
P0 moveto P1 P2 P3 curveto		%  draw Bezier curve
0.125 inch setlinewidth			%  fat line width
stroke					%  stroke the path
showpage				%  display page
